  <script>
   (function () {
            if ($('.socsupp-section').length) {
                var $soc_scrollerGrandWrapper = $('.socsupp-scroller-grand-wrapper');
                var $soc_scroller = $('.socsupp-scroller');
                var $soc_items = $('.socsupp-scroller__item');
                var soc_itemsL = $soc_items.length;
                var $soc_leftArrow = $soc_scrollerGrandWrapper.find('.socsupp-scroller-wrapper__left-arrow');
                var $soc_rightArrow = $soc_scrollerGrandWrapper.find('.socsupp-scroller-wrapper__right-arrow');
                var soc_step = 33.3333;
                var soc_onScreen = 3;
                var soc_curStep = 0;
                var soc_num = 0;



                function soc_countStep(soc_num) {
                    var before = soc_curStep + soc_num;
                    var nextStep = before >= 0 && (soc_onScreen + before <= soc_itemsL);

                    if (nextStep) {
                        soc_curStep = before;
                    }

                    return !nextStep;
                }

                function soc_nextStep(soc_num) {
                    var before = soc_curStep + soc_num;
                    var nextStep = before >= 0 && (soc_onScreen + before <= soc_itemsL);

                    return !nextStep;
                }

                function soc_setNewSize(newOnScreen, newSize) {
                    soc_step = newSize;
                    soc_onScreen = newOnScreen;
                    soc_curStep = 0;
                    soc_num = 0;

                    $soc_scroller.css('left', soc_num + '%');
                }

                function soc_showHideControls() {
                    if (soc_nextStep(-1)) {
                        $soc_leftArrow.addClass('hidden');
                    } else {
                        $soc_leftArrow.removeClass('hidden');
                    }

                    if (soc_nextStep(1)) {
                        $soc_rightArrow.addClass('hidden');
                    } else {
                        $soc_rightArrow.removeClass('hidden');
                    }
                }

                function soc_setVisibility() {
                    var visibleStart = soc_curStep + 1;
                    var visibleEnd = soc_curStep + soc_onScreen;

                    $soc_items.each(function (key, elem) {
                        var normKey = key + 1;

                        // Items that are currently in the main area become opaque
                        if (normKey >= visibleStart && normKey <= visibleEnd) {
                            $(elem).removeClass('transparent');
                            $(elem).addClass('opaque');
                        } else { // others become transparent
                            $(elem).removeClass('opaque');
                            $(elem).addClass('transparent');
                        }
                    });
                }

                $soc_leftArrow.on('click', function () {
                    if (soc_countStep(-1)) {
                        return false;
                    }

                    soc_num += soc_step;
                    $soc_scroller.css('left', soc_num + '%');
                    soc_showHideControls();
                    soc_setVisibility();
                });

                $soc_rightArrow.on('click', function () {
                    if (soc_countStep(1)) {
                        return false;
                    }

                    soc_num -= soc_step;
                    $soc_scroller.css('left', soc_num + '%');
                    soc_showHideControls();
                    soc_setVisibility();
                });


                $(window).on('resolution-change', function (event, soc_windowWidth) {
                    // Our slider has only three sizes and we don't need fourth
                    if (soc_windowWidth === 360) {
                        soc_windowWidth = 320;
                    }

                    if (soc_windowWidth !== 360) {
                        var pageSizes = {
                            // [numOfItems, percents]
                            '320': [1, 100],
                            '736': [2, 50],
                            '1088': [3, 33.3333],
                        };

                        var curSettings = pageSizes[soc_windowWidth];
                        soc_setNewSize(curSettings[0], curSettings[1]);
                        soc_setVisibility();
                        soc_showHideControls();
                    }
                });
            }
        })();
  </script>
